Ushahidi,is,a,non,profit,technology,company,specializing,in,developing,free,and,open,source,software,for,information,collection,visualization,and,interactive,mapping,Originally,developed,to,map,reports,of,violence,in,Kenya,after,the,post,election,fallout,in,early,the,organization,now,has,teams,of,volunteer,developers,in,Africa,Europe,South,America,and,the,U,S,The,Ushahidi,platform,allows,you,to,use,create,visualize,and,share,stories,on,an,interactive,map,With,the,Ushahidi,API,you,can,retrieve,reports,categories,locations,comments,countries,and,custom,forms,The,platform,s,REST,API,requests,are,submitted,trough,HTTP,GET,or,HTTP,Post,The,API,supports,both,XML,and,JSON,output,formats